text: "\n <div id=\"recipeLeftColumn\">\n  # Goofy Names\n  <hr/>\n  GoOfY NaMeS\n\
  \  <div id=\"recipeGoal\">\n   ## Goal:\n   Write an algorithm to change a String\
  \ into a \"goofy\" version.\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div id=\"recipeRightColumn\">\n\
  \  <div id=\"recipeSteps\">\n   ## Steps:\n   <ol id=\"stepList\">\n    <li>\n \
  \    Ask the user to enter their name.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Use a loop to\
  \ alternately modify each character of the name into uppercase and lowercase letters\
  \ until a new \"goofy\" representation of their name has been constructed.\n   \
  \  For example, if they enter their name as\n     <font color=\"green\">\n     \
  \ Alexander Hamilton\n     </font>\n     their goofy name will be\n     <font color=\"\
  green\">\n      AlExAnDeR HaMiLtOn\n     </font>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Show\
  \ the user the goofy version of their name in a pop-up.\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n \
  \ </div>\n </div>\n\n"
